Ogun Governor Dapo Abiodun has appointed #BigBrotherNaija season 5 winner, Olamilekan Agbeleshe aka Laycon as a youth ambassador. Abidoun made this known on Tuesday while receiving Laycon in his office. He said: “I personally look forward to working with you to be a model of good character, excellence, good virtue, calmness, integrity that are general attributes of Ogun State Government as a matter of fact, you’re from Odeda.” He further advised Laycon to channel his energies towards curbing vices, immoral acts among other things in the society.